    <html:p>You may access my <fr:link href="/0005/" title="Curriculum Vitæ" uri="https://sez.moe/0005/" display-uri="0005" type="local">Curriculum Vitæ</fr:link> here. My professional email is <html:code>ym2825@ic.ac.uk</html:code>. For contacts otherwise, please send email to <html:code>echo golf oscar at *this domain*</html:code>.</html:p>
    <html:p>Additionally, I maintain multiple social platform accounts under the same name as the <fr:link href="https://www.forester-notes.org/0073/index.xml" type="external">tree address</fr:link> of this page.</html:p>
