                <html:p>Additionally, I maintain multiple social platform accounts under the same name as the <fr:link href="https://www.forester-notes.org/0073/index.xml" type="external">tree address</fr:link> of this page.</html:p>
                <html:p>You may wish to access my personal Telegram channel via <fr:link href="https://t.me/pre_yoyogi" type="external">this link</fr:link></html:p>
