              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>My preferred name Yve (pronounced i-veh) is a transliteration of my Shanghainese first name Yiq-wê. My first name can also be written in Mandarin as Yiwei, or written in different <html:em>gender inflections</html:em> as Yvette or Yves. These names are all used under different occasions.</html:p>
