            <fr:title text="ヨよ木 (Yoyogi)">ヨよ木 (Yoyogi)</fr:title>
            <fr:meta name="orcid">0009-0008-0934-6821</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>I am Yve Meng. This is my personal website, realised as a <fr:link href="https://www.forester-notes.org/index/index.xml" type="external">forester space</fr:link>. You can find more information about me in my <fr:link href="/sezryo/" title="Yve Meng" uri="https://sez.moe/sezryo/" display-uri="sezryo" type="local">bio</fr:link>, or directly <fr:link href="/0006/" title="Contact me" uri="https://sez.moe/0006/" display-uri="0006" type="local">contact me</fr:link> for even further discussions.</html:p>
            <html:p>This website primarily serves as a research <fr:link href="/0002/" title="Notes" uri="https://sez.moe/0002/" display-uri="0002" type="local">note</fr:link> of my current studies. Additionally, my random thoughts are also posted here, making part of this website to be a casual blog.</html:p>
            <html:p>Pages of this site may be written in multiple or mixed languages.</html:p>
            <html:p>You may navigate this whole <fr:link href="https://www.forester-notes.org/index/index.xml" type="external">forester</fr:link> via <html:code>ctrl+K</html:code>.</html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors />
                <fr:uri>https://sez.moe/0001/</fr:uri>
                <fr:display-uri>0001</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/0001/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Name of this website">Name of this website</fr:title>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>The name ヨよ木 comes as a homonym of 代々木, a vibrant area in Tokyo. ヨ mimics the existence quantifier, よ is identified as the Yoneda functor, and 木 marks a place for inhabitance.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <html:p>You may find contents in the following <fr:link href="https://www.forester-notes.org/tfmt-000R/index.xml" type="external">trees</fr:link>: <fr:link href="/0002/" title="Notes" uri="https://sez.moe/0002/" display-uri="0002" type="local">notes</fr:link>, <fr:link href="/0003/" title="Articles" uri="https://sez.moe/0003/" display-uri="0003" type="local">articles</fr:link>, <fr:link href="/0004/" title="Thoughts" uri="https://sez.moe/0004/" display-uri="0004" type="local">thoughts</fr:link>, and my <fr:link href="/sezryo/" title="Yve Meng" uri="https://sez.moe/sezryo/" display-uri="sezryo" type="local">bio</fr:link>.</html:p>
